= Tamazoan = Gaga mniq Nantowseyn Sinyisyang ka alang Tamazoan. 322 sapah ka kneego na sapah, 1,109 hiyi ka kana knhbragan na hiyi. Tnposo seejiq o mangal 93% niqan 1,027 hiyi sp, rahoq na oxay tnposo seejiq o mangal 7% niqan 82 hiyi koia. Kana ka kleegan seejiq ga, Bonon 90%, Tayal 2%.
